    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315400/extras/7e75f7e5121075b77f66a4a357d8cd40.poster.avif?t=1766067770\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315400/extras/7e75f7e5121075b77f66a4a357d8cd40.webm?t=1766067770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315400/extras/7e75f7e5121075b77f66a4a357d8cd40.mp4?t=1766067770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《狭间骑士》是一款回合制战略游戏，和《狭间格斗》属于同一宇宙。本作独立成篇，承袭前作广受好评的玩法，融入创新巧思，带玩家一起穿越到中世纪。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315400/extras/bfe4472c5346899060d90657e9187799.poster.avif?t=1766067770\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315400/extras/bfe4472c5346899060d90657e9187799.webm?t=1766067770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>《狭间骑士》战斗部分充满了动作电影般的视觉效果和动画处理，冲击力十足。伴着电子乐的鼓点，用身手和头脑过关斩将，战出一条血路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315400/extras/ba60a43a114b5db571959d89e5fc3963.poster.avif?t=1766067770\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315400/extras/ba60a43a114b5db571959d89e5fc3963.webm?t=1766067770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>想要大获全胜，光靠一手好牌还不够，还要学会让环境为你所用。招募队员、集结队伍，玩转卡牌搭配，巧用招式组合，发挥一加一大于二的效果。不过务必谨记，选择谁、拒绝谁，都要仔细思量！因为有时候，做不成盟友的人，可能转眼就变成对手……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315400/extras/1ad0b921f476eee68afc3656f9f8abca.poster.avif?t=1766067770\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315400/extras/1ad0b921f476eee68afc3656f9f8abca.webm?t=1766067770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>《狭间骑士》内有 300 张卡牌，搭配各色职业和装备，再加上升级系统，约等于享之不尽的卡牌构筑乐趣。喜欢挑战的话，不妨在“每日游戏”排行榜上和其他玩家一较高下；如果想要突破自己的极限，可以去“无尽模式”接受试炼。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315400/extras/955b36ca75b7f17226646def5c51b0df.avif?t=1766067770\" width=616 height=167 /></span>",
